Title: Rejsol Salicylic acid 20% 50ml(50 ml)
Description: Salicylic Acid is a Anti Acne agent it penetrates the pores of the acne and kills the organisms.Chemical Peels are acids therefore should be used under the Supervision of trained cosmetologists.Always do Patch Test when using the peel for the first time.Patch test: Apply small amount of peel below neck or armpit, see for any redness beyond the margin of application, if seendiscontinue the procedure. If no redness or itching continue with the procedureProcedure:Cleanse the skin with oil free cleanser, if using oil containing cleanser, after cleansing whip with alcohol or spirit. oil blocks the acid therefore desired action is not achieved.Apply Peel with brush or ear Buds, gel peels can be best applied with gloved fingers. start applying from the forehead upto the neck, application time should not be more than 20 seconds. keep peel for 3-7 mins depending on your skin habituality of peeling and the peel strength. yellow peel can be kept for 10-30 mins. keep on yellow peel is kept overnight.Spray neutralizer, keep for 1 min.wash with water., apply sunscreen and good moisturiser.Post Peel:Sunprotection with atleast spf 50 sunscreen is very essential to get good resultsapply good moisturiser.success of the peeling depends on sunprotection and moisturisingfirst the skin dies so becomes black don't worry this is the skin that is going to peel of itselfThere are two types of peeling microscopic that is not seen by naked eyes, and macroscopic peeling that is visualised very wellDo not remove the skin by your self.Don't use soap for 2-3 days, thereafter, use mild soap for 7-8 days, don't scrub too hardNote: If you don't get desired results doesnt mean the peel is not working it only means that your skin is tough for the peel you are using. then its time to use stronger peels or increase the application time of the peel in the next sitting.

Easy to use when you go to the pool or beach or just under your day to day clothing. Tips - change the tampon every 4-8 hours or more often if needed. If after this time, white fibre is still visible, try a lower absorbency. The tampon can be more easily removed when fully saturated. A lot of women change the tampon too quickly because they are afraid of leakage. If worried, use a pantyliner for extra protection instead of removing the tampon when not fully saturated. Tampons can be worn over night but remember to insert a fresh tampon before going to sleep and change again first thing in the morning. Please read the leaflet inside of all helen harper packs. These tampons do not come with applicator.

Title: Hugo Boss Red 3 Piece Set for Men
Description: Revealing a manâ€™s dynamic and charismatic persona, Hugo Boss presents this extremely masculine fragrance that attracts the attention from everyone. Perfect for a man whose every stride exudes a virile air, this clean aromatic fragrance adds to his appeal. A Fresh and Sensual Scent Infusing freshness and sensuality, this perfume indulges you in a playful mood. This perfume flares up the carefree spirit in a man. Title: Burberry Summer - Set of 2 (2 x 100 ml) EDT  -  200 ml(For Women)
Ralph Lauren Polo Double Black EDT  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: A quintessential representation of the laid-back American way of life, Polo Double Black from the fashion house of Ralph Lauren is a masculine portrayal of ideal, casual elegance. Created as a simple yet enigmatic scent by perfumer Ellen Molner, this luxury Eau de Toilette is a provocative amalgamation of fresh, woody and oriental accords. Refreshing like the cool breeze that satiates the dry, arid land, and intoxicating like the sensuous aroma of spices in the Moroccan bazaar, Polo Black mingles a cool, breezy notes with the warmth of zesty base notes. Opening with a fresh top note of frozen mango, Polo Black trails into a heart of fried coffee, pepper and Indonesian nutmeg. An earthy base of fir is infused with cardamom to lend a hint of sensuality to this elixir. Encased in a miniature decanter with jet black matte finish and the iconic Ralph Lauren crest emblazoned on it, Polo Double Black perfectly captures the essence of a relaxed yet powerfully masculine persona.

Title: Dunhill London EDC  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: London, from the British fashion house of Dunhill, draws inspiration from the ever-moving vignettes of the charismatic city it is named after. Pleasing and refreshing at the same time, Dunhill London is the perfect signature perfume for the modern day gentleman. An enigmatic blend of the warm oriental fragrance and the captivating fougere scent, this luxury fragrance unquestionably defines elegance and desirability. The Dunhill London Eau de Toilette is an amalgamation of different ingredients which collectively signify an idea - a unity of the past and present, of timelessness and modernity. The refreshing scent of succulent apples dominates the vibrant top note and evokes a sense of energy. Deeply rooted in English tradition, the heart note of Damascus rose is a metaphor for the House of Roses from a glorious past. This is dexterously blended with a dark and mysterious base note of rich patchouli that produces a rich, wine-like depth. Official yet vibrant, this urbane fragrance is certain to impress at all occasions.

Title: Police Silver Wings EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: He texts his friend that he is on his way and swipes his smartcard at the station. He tweets that interesting bit of graffiti on a random wall and Facebooks his boredom away. He is a denizen of a world where everything is digital - his smartphone is his lifeline and he would be lost without his GPS tracker. He is the man who is the future of the species, one who the future generation looks up to. His cosmopolitan lifestyle and his charisma enamor the other gender of his species to whom he has always been an enigma. For the generation that infuses hope even into lost cause, the Italian house of Police presents Silver Wings, a fragrance that captures the essence of the signature brand. Be completely yourself and portray your multicultural tastes with the mass premium Eau de Toilette that never ceases to make you wonder at the various dimensions it has, just like you. Bold and blatantly contemporary, Police Silver Wings was launched in 2008. Opening notes which resound with the spicy accords of coriander and nutmeg. The heart notes calm you down with the herbaceousness of violet leaf. The slightly nutty resined accords of amber complement the powdery masculinity of musk that adds a warmth to the potion. Silver Wings is presented to the world in the charcoal black flacon, rectangular with bold cuts. The silver band on the top of the flacon sets of the black stopper and complement the delicate silver wings printed on the heart of the flacon. Embrace the uniqueness that makes you who you are, a person that so many people find fascinating with the smooth, suave tones of Police Silver Wings.

Description: For the natural, unconditional and the fierce man in you, this EDT from Police creates an enigmatic aura for your masculinity. Top Note Opening with a note of fantasy and mystery along with a hint of spice of pimento and cardamom, this EDT engulfs you into its distinctive fragrance. Heart Note Evolving into the delicate, subtle and magnetic notes of velvet, sage and geranium, this fragrance takes you in an all-new world. Base Note With sandalwood, amber and musk as the base notes, this EDT mesmerises you with its sweet, woody, graceful and energetic scent, keeping you fresh for long.

Launched by the established French perfume house Ulric de Varens, this luxury Eau de Parfum is designed for the essential woman in you, with her passions, emotions and vitality reflecting in her fashion choices.
